The CD2H leadership team gathered in beautiful Portland on the OHSU campus for a 2-day strategic planning session December 13-14. Site PIs and Working Group leads discussed topics like governance, communication,  working group launch and function, partnerships, timelines deliverables, and the CTSA Program, including the Informatics Domain Task Force.
The strategic planning sessions were a great opportunity for team building and incredibly productive. Stay tuned for more details and next steps!
&nbsp;

Melissa Haendel, CD2H Director, shared some exciting CD2H updates on the July 27 CTSA Site PI webinar. Please review the slides and listen to her talk to learn more about the CD2H’s approach to accelerating informatics innovation and three of the projects we currently have underway. We look forward to further  engagement with the community and as always, welcome your feedback and suggestions.
To watch the CD2H Update to the CTSA  P.I. Meeting on July 25, 2018 please forward to 15:35 on the video below.
